{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, if you're in the audience today,"},{"time":2000,"text":"or maybe you're watching this talk in some other time or place,"},{"time":5000,"text":"you are a participant in the digital rights ecosystem."},{"time":8000,"text":"Whether you're an artist, a technologist,"},{"time":10000,"text":"a lawyer or a fan,"},{"time":12000,"text":"the handling of copyright directly impacts your life."},{"time":15000,"text":"Rights management is no longer"},{"time":17000,"text":"simply a question of ownership,"},{"time":20000,"text":"it's a complex web of relationships"},{"time":22000,"text":"and a critical part of our cultural landscape."},{"time":25000,"text":"YouTube cares deeply about the rights of content owners,"},{"time":28000,"text":"but in order to give them choices about what they can do"},{"time":30000,"text":"with copies, mashups and more,"},{"time":33000,"text":"we need to first identify"},{"time":35000,"text":"when copyrighted material is uploaded to our site."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"Let's look at a specific video so you can see how it works."},{"time":41000,"text":"Two years ago, recording artist Chris Brown"},{"time":43000,"text":"released the official video of his single \"Forever.\""},{"time":46000,"text":"A fan saw it on TV,"},{"time":48000,"text":"recorded it with her camera phone,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and uploaded it to YouTube."},{"time":53000,"text":"Because Sony Music had registered Chris Brown's video"},{"time":56000,"text":"in our Content ID system,"},{"time":58000,"text":"within seconds of attempting to upload the video,"},{"time":60000,"text":"the copy was detected,"},{"time":62000,"text":"giving Sony the choice of what to do next."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"But how do we know that the user's video was a copy?"},{"time":68000,"text":"Well, it starts with content owners"},{"time":70000,"text":"delivering assets into our database,"},{"time":72000,"text":"along with a usage policy"},{"time":74000,"text":"that tells us what to do when we find a match."},{"time":78000,"text":"We compare each upload"},{"time":80000,"text":"against all of the reference files in our database."},{"time":83000,"text":"This heat map is going to show you"},{"time":85000,"text":"how the brain of the system works."},{"time":87000,"text":"Here we can see the original reference file"},{"time":89000,"text":"being compared to the user generated content."},{"time":93000,"text":"The system compares every moment"},{"time":95000,"text":"of one to the other to see if there's a match."},{"time":97000,"text":"This means that we can identify a match"},{"time":99000,"text":"even if the copy used is just a portion of the original file,"},{"time":102000,"text":"plays it in slow motion"},{"time":104000,"text":"and has degraded audio and video quality."},{"time":107000,"text":"And we do this every time"},{"time":109000,"text":"that a video is uploaded to YouTube."},{"time":111000,"text":"And that's over 20 hours of video every minute."},{"time":114000,"text":"When we find a match,"},{"time":116000,"text":"we apply the policy that the rights owner has set down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"And the scale and the speed of this system"},{"time":123000,"text":"is truly breathtaking."},{"time":125000,"text":"We're not just talking about a few videos,"},{"time":128000,"text":"we're talking about over"},{"time":130000,"text":"100 years of video every day,"},{"time":133000,"text":"between new uploads and the legacy scans"},{"time":135000,"text":"we regularly do across all of the content on the site."},{"time":139000,"text":"When we compare those hundred years of video,"},{"time":141000,"text":"we're comparing it against millions"},{"time":143000,"text":"of reference files in our database."},{"time":145000,"text":"It would be like 36,000 people"},{"time":147000,"text":"staring at 36,000 monitors"},{"time":150000,"text":"each and every day, without so much as a coffee break."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"Now, what do we do when we find a match?"},{"time":156000,"text":"Well, most rights owners, instead of blocking,"},{"time":159000,"text":"will allow the copy to be published."},{"time":161000,"text":"And then they benefit through the exposure,"},{"time":163000,"text":"advertising and linked sales."},{"time":166000,"text":"Remember Chris Brown's video \"Forever\"?"},{"time":168000,"text":"Well, it had its day in the sun and then it dropped off the charts,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and that looked like the end of the story,"},{"time":173000,"text":"but sometime last year, a young couple got married."},{"time":175000,"text":"This is their wedding video."},{"time":177000,"text":"You may have seen it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"What's amazing about this is,"},{"time":183000,"text":"if the processional of the wedding was this much fun,"},{"time":185000,"text":"can you imagine how much fun the reception must have been?"},{"time":187000,"text":"I mean, who are these people?"},{"time":189000,"text":"I totally want to go to that wedding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"So their little wedding video went on"},{"time":194000,"text":"to get over 40 million views."},{"time":197000,"text":"And instead of Sony blocking,"},{"time":199000,"text":"they allowed the upload to occur."},{"time":201000,"text":"And they put advertising against it"},{"time":203000,"text":"and linked from it to iTunes."},{"time":205000,"text":"And the song, 18 months old,"},{"time":208000,"text":"went back to number four on the iTunes charts."},{"time":211000,"text":"So Sony is generating revenue from both of these."},{"time":214000,"text":"And Jill and Kevin, the happy couple,"},{"time":216000,"text":"they came back from their honeymoon"},{"time":218000,"text":"and found that their video had gone crazy viral."},{"time":220000,"text":"And they've ended up on a bunch of talk shows,"},{"time":223000,"text":"and they've used it as an opportunity to make a difference."},{"time":225000,"text":"The video's inspired over 26,000 dollars in donations"},{"time":228000,"text":"to end domestic violence."},{"time":230000,"text":"The \"JK Wedding [Entrance] Dance\" became so popular"},{"time":233000,"text":"that NBC parodied it on the season finale of \"The Office,\""},{"time":236000,"text":"which just goes to show,"},{"time":238000,"text":"it's truly an ecosystem of culture."},{"time":241000,"text":"Because it's not just amateurs borrowing from big studios,"},{"time":244000,"text":"but sometimes big studios borrowing back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"By empowering choice, we can create a culture of opportunity."},{"time":250000,"text":"And all it took to change things around"},{"time":252000,"text":"was to allow for choice through rights identification."},{"time":255000,"text":"So why has no one ever solved this problem before?"},{"time":258000,"text":"It's because it's a big problem,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and it's complicated and messy."},{"time":262000,"text":"It's not uncommon for a single video"},{"time":264000,"text":"to have multiple rights owners."},{"time":266000,"text":"There's musical labels."},{"time":268000,"text":"There's multiple music publishers."},{"time":270000,"text":"And each of these can vary by country."},{"time":272000,"text":"There's lots of cases"},{"time":274000,"text":"where we have more than one work mashed together."},{"time":276000,"text":"So we have to manage many claims"},{"time":278000,"text":"to the same video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280000,"text":"YouTube's Content ID system addresses all of these cases."},{"time":283000,"text":"But the system only works through"},{"time":285000,"text":"the participation of rights owners."},{"time":287000,"text":"If you have content that others are uploading to YouTube,"},{"time":290000,"text":"you should register in the Content ID system,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and then you'll have the choice"},{"time":294000,"text":"about how your content is used."},{"time":296000,"text":"And think carefully about the policies that you attach to that content."},{"time":299000,"text":"By simply blocking all reuse,"},{"time":301000,"text":"you'll miss out on new art forms,"},{"time":303000,"text":"new audiences,"},{"time":305000,"text":"new distribution channels"},{"time":307000,"text":"and new revenue streams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"But it's not just about dollars and impressions."},{"time":312000,"text":"Just look at all the joy"},{"time":314000,"text":"that was spread through progressive rights management"},{"time":316000,"text":"and new technology."},{"time":318000,"text":"And I think we can all agree that joy is definitely an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":323000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}